{"tid":761425,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[學術] 講下左同右(handedness) 一 人體不對稱","createTime":"2018-07-30T11:23:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T11:51:59.000Z","uid":147721,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e370ded805a8ea9e0bb6fd042efa5b3651e46be4","tid":761425,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T11:23:59.000Z","msg":"開始之前先講明三點<br />\n1. 講下 唔包啱 唔包論述完整 歡迎討論同補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2. <strong><ins>唔好引用長文</ins></strong> 要針對特定內容回覆 請務必用編輯引用 淨係引你想引既野 我之前啲po已經因爲長引文搞到好亂<br />\n3. 我有嚴重走數傾向 目前拖緊拉格朗日力學 細電 同埋顏色既po 呢個系列都好有可能無啦啦休刊十年 有興趣睇既巴打自己留意返風險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上星期係學術台有個po問關於左右撇 激起左我既興趣 所以就開po講下了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一個po首先講下人體既不對稱同少少故事先 唔會有深入既野<br />\n<br />\n人最明顯既左右不對稱性 相信大家數到三個<br />\n1. 內臟既不對稱<br />\n2. 腦功能既不對稱<br />\n3. 偏手性<br />\n<br />\n講到內臟既不對稱 相信大家即刻會講個心係左邊<br />\n喇 呢個講法係唔精準既 甚至可以話好誤導<br />\n你諗下 你個心有成個拳頭咁大 個心係左邊既 你個左肺要點擺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我比較中意講 心臟在中間 心尖扭向左<br />\n不過呢啲文字遊戲唔係呢個po既重點<br />\n除左心臟向左之外 仲有肝係右 脾係左<br />\n好多人學過但唔記得既 係左邊肺有兩塊肺葉 右邊有三塊<br />\n而大部分人唔知既 係右邊睪丸高過左邊睪丸 而且右邊比較大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當然 人體咁神奇 實冇絕對既<br />\n有少數人有內臟逆位 個心尖扭向右 咩都同一般人相反<br />\n不過佢地除左內臟左右相反之外 其他野同一般人無異<br />\n唯一好處就係開槍打佢右腹唔會爆肝而死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02ede971581b6c90333b456c082232f9a99e663e","tid":761425,"uid":179571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T11:33:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"205c538f808d21cd42f81e8783fa1a1c041fdb27","tid":761425,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T11:34:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4c93494a0100e40c1fe7963c13a12f27cbef3ca","tid":761425,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T11:39:11.000Z","msg":"然後就到腦功能<br />\n相信大家而家聽到話咩左腦負責語言 肯定會覺得挑又係奶粉商呃媽媽<br />\n無可否認奶粉商啲廣告係誇張既 但係大部分人既某啲語言功能真係係左腦<br />\n點解咁講呢 因為我地有大量既頭部/腦損傷病例 失語症患者 有左腦損傷既遠比有右腦損傷既多<br />\n<br />\n當然啦 凡事都有例外 唔係人人既語言區都係左腦 語言區既損傷亦有可能有其他腦區可以取代佢既功能<br />\n不過根據一個十九世紀 sample size=46既統計<br />\n個組合係咁既(手機劣排版<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash; 失語 未失語<br />\n左腦受傷 15____6<br />\n右腦受傷 5____20<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後就係偏手性喇<br />\n偏手性唔係單單講手 腳呀眼呀都可以討論慣用邊隻<br />\n不過我地簡化下個焦點 集中講偏手性<br />\n左撇既人佔10-15%左右<br />\n左撇最慘係無較剪用 因為同筷子呀叉呀唔同 較剪本身唔係左右對稱既 用右手拎係可以好自然咁夾緊刀片 左手就要特別注意先夾得緊"},{"pid":"68860fe485ae5cf1c0ab6417f4716624b45add2b","tid":761425,"uid":138482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T11:51:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e4852c1f02f6bcd7aa9dfef62bc172a03123d7d","tid":761425,"uid":193131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T11:54:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 左右開弓的人留名"},{"pid":"acd11af720f04eed6507357924b33adf84e684f3","tid":761425,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T11:57:24.000Z","msg":"好 講到呢到 我地就有兩個好吸引既理論 望落可以好簡單解決左撇點黎既問題<br />\n<br />\n理論1 內臟逆位咪左撇囉<br />\n嗯 sor9 唔係<br />\n1950年johan torgerson 有篇x光檢查肺結核既研究 順便研究埋呢樣野<br />\n998862個受試者入面 有122個內臟逆位<br />\n加上佢其他接觸到既70個內臟逆位 扣走佢唔清楚偏手性既<br />\n160個sample入面 得11個左撇<br />\n<br />\n理論2<br />\n左腦語言區咪右撇 右腦語言區咪左撇<br />\n嗯 有趣 語言區同偏手性有關聯 但唔係咁既簡單關聯<br />\n數據大概係咁(我未查證個數據既真實性 就咁引用書<br />\n______左語言____右語言<br />\n右撇_~95%_____~5%<br />\n左撇_~70%____~30%<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好 兩個簡單理論收了皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"406079715f54f5333fd2da5d465eaa761b7364ba","tid":761425,"uid":147721,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T12:07:08.000Z","msg":"咁當然仲有好多好吸引既理論 例如有人會覺得 係後天教育到咁既 多人用右手咪多右撇囉<br />\n不過唔係咁 如果真係咁既話 啲偏遠小島呀個啲同國際社會無聯繫既部落 比我地發現個時 應該大約一半部落多右撇 另一半部落就多左撇<br />\n不過現實係多右撇幾乎係放緒四海皆準<br />\n<br />\n呢個系列既po 之後會由各個角度去講下左同右 如果我唔走數既話<br />\n未必個個角度都有答案 更多既係推測 畢竟呢個係好闊好深既課題 仲有待研究同實證<br />\n其他角度包括文字 語言 物理 化學 生理 等等等等<br />\n<br />\n第一個po既最後戴返頭盔 我都係睇書睇返黎<br />\n本書叫右手左手 推薦大家可以買返本看門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cca37f20eb166dc1dba271ef8bec0ae0b3736389","tid":761425,"uid":135265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T12:16:34.000Z","msg":"留名學嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51a8331f2d7f392d9990c896ee445270aa112914","tid":761425,"uid":73463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T12:27:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee4bc3363527bd7ef157418a9bbc6fe7ee2c1f08","tid":761425,"uid":154402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T14:37:24.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"980e8b829a6c1702d7b44b1c6658953c20522fe6","tid":761425,"uid":30185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T14:46:33.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"74bc4d14745fd69ae0c2309c1162443698dc0dfa","tid":761425,"uid":5150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T02:46:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"975750b206dca5431c192d86b69008e4bae39102","tid":761425,"uid":24139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T13:01:28.000Z","msg":"樓豬摩牙啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"755d2225a032ecd2b6c0bc1e6c447f755fd2f99b","tid":761425,"uid":135265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T16:09:45.000Z","msg":"樓豬去咗邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13ebc4e9e92d7261c30c8573e6d56dd3b716d9be","tid":761425,"uid":121610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T16:51:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主"},{"pid":"2fcb4d666c7944cd1a9ec2981fa1af59ef012185","tid":761425,"uid":5150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T11:51:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}